Langa police are looking for anyone who has information which can lead to the arrest of four armed suspects who robbed a group of tourists on Malamba Street, Settlers Way, opposite Joe Slovo, last Wednesday at about 2pm.The male suspects were driving a grey/charcoal Chevrolet Spark vehicle. The police are pleading for anyone with information can please contact Detective Sergeant Dalasa at 021 695 8000 or 078 958 5825.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.